{"id":56188,"date":"2021-06-29T09:34:54","date_gmt":"2021-06-29T08:34:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?p=56188"},"modified":"2021-07-07T13:10:16","modified_gmt":"2021-07-07T12:10:16","slug":"plastic-alternatives-zero-waste","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/plastic-alternatives-zero-waste\/","title":{"rendered":"Plastic Product Alternatives: 7 Easy Ways to go Zero-Waste!"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2 id=\"h-zero-waste-alternatives-to-plastic\">Zero Waste alternatives to Plastic<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As technology advances, loads of great plastic alternatives are being produced. Many of these are recyclable (such as glass or cardboard), biodegradable (bamboo or wood), or even edible (packaging made from mushrooms or seaweed)! Whether it&#x2019;s at home, at work, or on vacation, we&#x2019;ve got you covered with a complete list of alternatives to plastic products.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2-1080x738.jpg\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"308\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\" class=\"wp-image-60409 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2-1080x738.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2-800x547.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2-450x308.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2-163x111.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2-263x180.jpg 263w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2-768x525.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2-1024x700.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2-1440x984.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2-300x205.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2-600x410.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2-30x21.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085142\/zero-waste-soap-bar-2-1080x738.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-home-products-plastic-alternatives\"><strong>Home<\/strong> Products Plastic Alternatives<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The first easy change you can make is by finding plastic alternatives for your home life. There is a surprising amount of single-use plastic used for household items such as laundry detergent, dish soap, and trash bags. Instead, use:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Powdered laundry detergent:<\/strong> Buy it in a recyclable cardboard box at the supermarket or use a refillable option online.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Liquid dish soap<\/strong>: Lots of zero-waste shops now offer a refill section for dish soap and detergent. You can even buy a special <a href=\"https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/No-Tox-Life-Washing-Block\/dp\/B082LPCF4M?dchild=1&amp;keywords=dish+soap+vegan&amp;qid=1620467064&amp;sr=8-2&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=saltinourha06-20&amp;linkId=9a5c7a95c0c6c595d959fdd4ab8a9dd3&amp;language=en_US&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">eco-friendly soap<\/a> to wash your dishes.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Glass Tupperware:<\/strong> Put your leftover food in the fridge in glass containers, rather than covering it in plastic wrap. You can also buy silicone food covers <a href=\"https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Silicone-Expandable-Eco-Friendly-Microwave-Dishwasher\/dp\/B07VQWHN4Y?dchild=1&amp;keywords=silicone+food+covers&amp;qid=1619102572&amp;sr=8-1-spons&amp;psc=1&amp;spLa=ZW5jcnlwdGVkUXVhbGlmaWVyPUExTzY0UUFWQzhJTVZXJmVuY3J5cHRlZElkPUEwNTUyNTgzMkM0TUNLWFZPQTdKMCZlbmNyeXB0ZWRBZElkPUEwMjMwNjIwMlVUTUZHWkZCSzVLTyZ3aWRnZXROYW1lPXNwX2F0ZiZhY3Rpb249Y2xpY2tSZWRpcmVjdCZkb05vdExvZ0NsaWNrPXRydWU%3D&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=saltinourha06-20&amp;linkId=1c73a613b4a4153f0f2ad03f3ccec165&amp;language=en_US&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">like these<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2.jpg\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\" class=\"wp-image-60407 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2-1440x961.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2-600x400.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085133\/zero-waste-bali-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Newspaper:<\/strong> Use newspaper to line your bin, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B009O7P61S?th=1&amp;psc=1&amp;ascsubtag=5097468%7Cn16b103e7abbd404d97beecb14f84b84014&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=saltinourha06-20&amp;linkId=6faad5e09114599c20f2636f3e243e26&amp;language=en_US&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">buy biodegradable trash bags<\/a>, or don&#x2019;t use trash bags at all. Do not add any food waste in the biodegradable trash bags, as they will dissolve faster. Instead, separate your food compost in a smaller bin without a trash bag that you can easily empty and clean after a few days.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Toilet paper\/Kitchen paper alternatives<\/strong>: Choose a recycled toilet paper and use reusable napkins\/cloths instead of kitchen paper. At least don&#x2019;t buy toilet paper that has colored drawings on it, as these are even worse for recycling!<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/56188&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/18092256\/plastic-alternatives3.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.