440.jpg 1779w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local-30x24.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/23121432\/sustainable-travel-shop-local.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<ul><li><strong>Use your own glass\/metal\/bamboo containers<\/strong> when shopping for food. For example, for your fruit and veg. Look for a supermarket that offers a refill service (these are becoming more and more popular as an alternative to plastic).<\/li><li><strong>Choose foods without plastic packaging.<\/strong> For instance, avoid buying juices and other bottled drinks, as well as condiments and sauces that come in plastic packaging. It pushes you to make your own and be healthier too!<\/li><li><strong>Avoid buying bottled water.<\/strong> Most of the time, water is totally fine to drink from the tap. If, however, you live in a country where it&#x2019;s not, then consider buying a water purifier\/filter. <br>Another option is to buy water cartridges that are refillable.&#xA0;We have seen this in supermarkets in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Italy<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Portugal<\/a>.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2.jpg\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\" class=\"wp-image-60413 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2-1440x961.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2-600x400.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085555\/plastic-alternatives2-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-when-online-shopping\">When online shopping:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Shop online from local stores<\/strong> to minimize delivery emissions.<\/li><li><strong>Choose compostable packaging.<\/strong> Look to order from sustainable businesses that don&#x2019;t use plastic to package their products. For example, they might use recycled cardboard or compostable materials.&#xA0;<\/li><li><strong>Look for companies that have plastic-free initiatives.<\/strong> This could be beach clean-ups, recycling programs, or clothing that is actually made from recycled plastic.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17084908\/easy-tips-travel-plastic-free-2-1080x786.jpg\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"327\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\" class=\"wp-image-60376 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17084908\/easy-tips-travel-plastic-free-2-1080x786.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17084908\/easy-tips-travel-plastic-free-2-800x582.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17084908\/easy-tips-travel-plastic-free-2-450x327.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17084908\/easy-tips-travel-plastic-free-2-30x22.jpg 30w, htt