d toiletries. For example:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"h-make-up-wipes-cleanser\"><strong>Make-up wipes\/cleanser<\/strong>: Instead of using throw-away wipes that usually contain plastic and come in plastic packaging, choose <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/plastic-free-makeupremover\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">reusable makeup pads<\/a> and cleansers. This is not only better for the environment, but it&#x2019;ll save you money! Wash the pads after use and choose a face soap that comes in a bar. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085027\/reduce-plastic-washable-makeup-flannel-2.jpg\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"304\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\" class=\"wp-image-60393 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085027\/reduce-plastic-washable-makeup-flannel-2.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085027\/reduce-plastic-washable-makeup-flannel-2-800x541.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085027\/reduce-plastic-washable-makeup-flannel-2-1080x731.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085027\/reduce-plastic-washable-makeup-flannel-2-450x304.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085027\/reduce-plastic-washable-makeup-flannel-2-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085027\/reduce-plastic-washable-makeup-flannel-2-163x110.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085027\/reduce-plastic-washable-makeup-flannel-2-266x180.jpg 266w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/202