ers.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Reusable coffee cup: <\/strong>Sometimes, we might not even realize how many coffee cups we are throwing away per day. This way, you can take your coffee with you wherever you go and save the planet!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Reusable straws:<\/strong> Buy a reusable straw that you keep with you to use for drinks, or don&#x2019;t use a straw at all.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085545\/plastic-alternatives1-2.jpg\" alt=\"plastic alternatives straw\"><\/noscript><img width=\"240\" height=\"338\" alt=\"plastic alternatives straw\" class=\"wp-image-60411 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1362px) 100vw, 1362px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085545\/plastic-alternatives1-2.jpg 1362w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085545\/plastic-alternatives1-2-426x600.jpg 426w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085545\/plastic-alternatives1-2-575x810.jpg 575w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085545\/plastic-alternatives1-2-240x338.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085545\/plastic-alternatives1-2-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085545\/plastic-alternatives1-2-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085545\/plastic-alternatives1-2-128x180.jpg 128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085545\/plastic-alternatives1-2-545x768.jpg 545w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085545\/plastic-alternatives1-2-726x1024.jpg 726w,