t comes in compostable packaging or a reusable tin.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Did you know? That most sunscreens are harmful to the corals? Read all about&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reef-safe-sunscreen\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">reef-safe sunscreen<\/a>&#xA0;here.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17084940\/plastic-free-Natural-cosmetics-2.jpg\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\"><\/noscript><img width=\"231\" height=\"338\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\" class=\"wp-image-60382 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1313px) 100vw, 1313px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17084940\/plastic-free-Natural-cosmetics-2.jpg 1313w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17084940\/plastic-free-Natural-cosmetics-2-410x600.jpg 410w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17084940\/plastic-free-Natural-cosmetics-2-554x810.jpg 554w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17084940\/plastic-free-Natural-cosmetics-2-231x338.jpg 231w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17084940\/plastic-free-Natural-cosmetics-2-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17084940\/plastic-free-Natural-cosmetics-2-111x163.jpg 111w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-conte