raw\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Life Straw<\/a>) to avoid using unnecessary plastic.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/plastic-free-bottle\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get your reusable water bottle<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2.jpg\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\"><\/noscript><img width=\"244\" height=\"338\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\" class=\"wp-image-60403 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1384px) 100vw, 1384px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2.jpg 1384w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2-433x600.jpg 433w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2-584x810.jpg 584w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2-244x338.jpg 244w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2-117x163.jpg 117w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2-130x180.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2-554x768.jpg 554w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2-738x1024.jpg 738w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2-779x1080.jpg 779w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2-1038x1440.jpg 1038w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2-300x416.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2-600x832.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2-22x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085113\/travel-plastic-free-reusable-bottle-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Bring your own food on the airplane<\/strong>. Plane food comes in lots of plastic, so avoid it by saying &#x2018;no&#x2019; to airplane food and eating your own food instead. It&#x2019;ll be healthier too!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Reusable cutlery\/container\/straw<\/strong>: The likelihood is you&#x2019;ll be eating out a lot while traveling. Combat this by bringing reusable items with you for eating.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:&#xA0;<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reduce-plastic-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">13 Easy Tips to Travel Plastic-Free<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-why-is-plastic-so-bad-for-the-environment\">Why is Plastic so Bad for the Environment?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As we become more aware of the effects of climate change, we understand the harmful effects of plastic on planet earth. It can take up to 500 years to decompose, and in that time, it&#x2019;s likely to end up in oceans, in the bellies of sea life, and, eventually, even in our food chain. There are many reasons why we should choose plastic alternatives. For example:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>During a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.exeter.ac.uk\/news\/research\/title_695428_en.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">survey<\/a> of over 100 sea turtles (different species and different oceans), 100% of them had plastic in their stomachs.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.sas.org.uk\/our-work\/plastic-pollution\/plastic-pollution-facts-figures\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">8 million pieces<\/a> of plastic end up in the ocean every day.<\/li><li>Every minute, over <a href=\"https:\/\/www.theguardian.com\/environment\/2017\/jun\/28\/a-million-a-minute-worlds-plastic-bottle-binge-as-dangerous-as-climate-change\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">1 million plastic bottles<\/a> are bought worldwide.<\/li><li>The Great Pacific Garbage Patch, a floating mass of plastic off California, is twice the size of Texas!<\/li><li>Plastic is toxic for human health, and unknowingly, we ingest it. In fact, studies show that <a href=\"https:\/\/advocacy.consumerreports.org\/research\/bpa-factsheet\/#:~:text=How%20are%20we%20exposed%3F,into%20our%20systems%20when%20consumed.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">93% of Americans have BPA in their bodies<\/a> (a chemical used to make plastic).<\/li><li>Plastic production has <a href=\"https:\/\/www.weforum.org\/agenda\/2018\/03\/8-steps-to-solve-the-oceans-plastic-problem\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><em>doubled<\/em><\/a> over the last 50 years.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085044\/travel-plastic-free-beach-clean-up_-582x810.jpg\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\"><\/noscript><img width=\"243\" height=\"338\" alt=\"plastic alternatives\" data-id=\"60397\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085044\/travel-plastic-free-beach-clean-up_.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=60397\" class=\"wp-image-60397 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 582px) 100vw, 582px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085044\/travel-plastic-free-beach-clean-up_-582x810.jpg 582w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085044\/travel-plastic-free-beach-clean-up_-431x600.jpg 431w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/17085044\/travel-plastic-free-beach-clean-up_-243x338.jpg 2